<p class="ko" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">출처: 코인데스크(CoinDesk, "Battle over blockchain stock ownership is heading to Washington regulators"; "Securitize (SECZ) takes $295M of its own tokenized stock to Solana, Avalanche amid NYSE debut"), 코인스피커(Coin Speaker, "SEC Faces Wall Street Pressure as Transfer Agents Challenge External Token Models"), 비트코인 매거진(Bitcoin Magazine, "Transfer Agents Push Back on Tokenization Risks, Urge SEC to Protect Market Integrity"), PYMNTS.com("Regulators Hear Arguments on Tokenized Stock Ownership"), 데커트(Dechert, "SEC Staff Maps Tokenization Models: Tokenized Securities are Still Securities; Models Matter"), 미국 증권거래위원회(SEC, "Statement on Tokenized Securities"). 수치는 각 매체 보도 시점 기준 근사치다.</p>
<p class="en" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">Sources: CoinDesk ("Battle over blockchain stock ownership is heading to Washington regulators"; "Securitize (SECZ) takes $295M of its own tokenized stock to Solana, Avalanche amid NYSE debut"), Coin Speaker ("SEC Faces Wall Street Pressure as Transfer Agents Challenge External Token Models"), Bitcoin Magazine ("Transfer Agents Push Back on Tokenization Risks, Urge SEC to Protect Market Integrity"), PYMNTS.com ("Regulators Hear Arguments on Tokenized Stock Ownership"), Dechert ("SEC Staff Maps Tokenization Models: Tokenized Securities are Still Securities; Models Matter"), U.S. Securities and Exchange Commission ("Statement on Tokenized Securities"). Figures are approximate as of each outlet's reporting time.</p>
<p class="ja" style="font-size:12px;color:#52525b;margin-top:24px">出典: コインデスク(CoinDesk、「Battle over blockchain stock ownership is heading to Washington regulators」、「Securitize (SECZ) takes $295M of its own tokenized stock to Solana, Avalanche amid NYSE debut」)、コインスピーカー(Coin Speaker、「SEC Faces Wall Street Pressure as Transfer Agents Challenge External Token Models」)、ビットコイン・マガジン(Bitcoin Magazine、「Transfer Agents Push Back on Tokenization Risks, Urge SEC to Protect Market Integrity」)、PYMNTS.com(「Regulators Hear Arguments on Tokenized Stock Ownership」)、デカート(Dechert、「SEC Staff Maps Tokenization Models: Tokenized Securities are Still Securities; Models Matter」)、米証券取引委員会(SEC、「Statement on Tokenized Securities」)。数値は各媒体の報道時点の近似値である。</p>
